column5: So I had a school project to document a lifestyle, naturally I decided to do it on fishing! I have joined a bass fishing club this year decided to have my main focus on tournament fishing. I thought some people on here might like to see it, so here's the link! Also if your internet connection is good, be sure to watch it in HD!
excellent quality and a good prom for the tournament types
Great video Ryan! Too bad we didn't have a camera man last sun it would have been epic!Good job buddy!
LOVE IT !!!! great job and the choice of music intro fits it like a glove.I AM IRONMAN..... THANKS FOR SHARING
Very impressed great job Diltsy Richard
Great vid! I too am lookin to join a Bass club. Tried for two years and ran into problems. I'm hoping this is the year!
Excellent video Diltsy Thanks for sharing Leechman

Thanks guys! Wayne, we could have ten tapes full of good video from that day! So many fish!! Johnny Bass, I waited two yaers before joining my club... I guarantee when you join, you will regret not joining sooner! Hope to get some more shooting done next year, maybe get some ice fishing videos up!

Awesome video I belong to a Bass Club here in Toronto, best decision I have ever made. There are a few new members from this board that have joined as well. My best reason for joining. Learning and teaching and we get to go out and do stuff with kids to properly teach them how to fish and respect this hunting and fishing and the great outdoors.
